title: Armina major
text: Armina major is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20slug">sea slug</a>, a <a href="nudibranch">nudibranch</a>, a <a href="marine%20%28ocean%29">marine</a> <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the family <a href="Arminidae">Arminidae</a>.
